{"tid":1243193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（尋人）發夢特首辦見到一個戴某國國旗帽女神","createTime":"2019-06-19T10:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T19:11:52.000Z","uid":265333,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc113239b9433536756a21a4c50dba3bc19af3f","tid":1243193,"uid":265333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"近來咁多晚我都有份發夢<br />\n有一個夢我總係諗住 所以分享一下 睇下有冇機會搵番夢裏人<br />\n<br />\n有次發夢 深夜時分喺特首辦見到有個戴某國國旗帽 孭某運動品牌索袋嘅女手足 一個人坐喺龍和隧道口 <br />\n本來諗住行過去傾偈 <br />\n但係轉過頭就唔見咗佢 行咗圈都見唔返 <br />\n<br />\n事關我夜晚都會係添馬公園嗰頭hea<br />\n如果有機會希望可以喺佢坐嗰度見返佢；（"},{"pid":"44ad0c680319b765437a954b701658fca1990297","tid":1243193,"uid":212436,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"搵食躝埋一二邊啦 大家做緊正經嘢"},{"pid":"856b3ccc48e710fe7e8297662f8eca548b68e046","tid":1243193,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T19:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61Yvkj6TylL._UX466_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61Yvkj6TylL._UX466_.jpg&h=d806c779&s={SIZE}\" />我都見到個咁"}]}